// Data Visualization (10 components)
// ----------------------------------
// ProgressBar      - Linear progress with label, value, colors, sizes
// ProgressCircle   - Circular/ring progress using SVG
// ProgressSteps    - Horizontal step indicator (step 1 of 4 style)
// Timeline         - Vertical event timeline with dates, icons, content
// Gantt            - Simple CSS-based Gantt chart for projects
// Calendar         - Full month calendar view with events
// CalendarMini     - Small compact month view widget
// ScheduleView     - Week/day schedule with time slots
// KanbanBoard      - Drag-drop columns (Todo, In Progress, Done)
// TreeView         - File/folder tree structure with icons, expand/collapse

// Media Display (3 components)
// ----------------------------
// ImageGallery     - Image grid with lightbox modal on click
// VideoPlayer      - Video with custom controls (play, pause, volume, fullscreen)
// DocumentViewer   - Document preview card for PDF/DOC with download

